    "name": "Cosmic Cowboy Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3268500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/d29da1fb85683d60b48aae449f0349fa.avif?t=1729071323\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras_big/d29da1fb85683d60b48aae449f0349fa.avif?t=1729071323 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield full control in this sci-fi tactical turn-based game, featuring skill progression. Create the ultimate build, specialise in different ability classes, and overpower your enemies. Take control of the charismatic mercenary, Cowboy in the far future as he brings down an insidious corporation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Demo Key Features:</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tutorial level/level 1.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level 2.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately 1 - 2 hours of gameplay (depending on skill level)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill selection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based combat within a sci-fi western setting.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based combat inspired by XCOM and the original Fallout, Cosmic Cowboy brings a <strong>strategic</strong> and <strong>thought-provoking</strong> twist to this combat genre, with <strong>various abilities</strong> and <strong>enemy types</strong> for these mechanics to interact with.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/ec393335bbf1fae676584ba295795264.poster.avif?t=1729071323\" width=800 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/ec393335bbf1fae676584ba295795264.webm?t=1729071323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/ec393335bbf1fae676584ba295795264.mp4?t=1729071323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a fusion of <strong>neon</strong> and <strong>Western aesthetics</strong>, Cosmic Cowboy aims to bring a bold new visual flare to the turn-based genre, with a carefully curated appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/7fe31da0ea0625accaf6aa207b6113c6.poster.avif?t=1729071323\" width=800 height=122 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/7fe31da0ea0625accaf6aa207b6113c6.webm?t=1729071323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/7fe31da0ea0625accaf6aa207b6113c6.mp4?t=1729071323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring a diverse cast of characters, <strong>fully voiced</strong>, to help bring the world of Cosmic Cowboy to life and to help immerse you fully in this compelling narrative experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/45e3fde72b5ec162132416504adc1427.poster.avif?t=1729071323\" width=800 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/45e3fde72b5ec162132416504adc1427.webm?t=1729071323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/45e3fde72b5ec162132416504adc1427.mp4?t=1729071323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customise over <strong>5 different skills</strong> and choose from <strong>3 different classes</strong> to make each play unique. Each allows every play-through to open up other aspects of attack and tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/978e3a94b0c3eb13c3cf2b32fd801292.webp?t=1729071323\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268500/extras/978e3a94b0c3eb13c3cf2b32fd801292.poster.avif?t=1729071323\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=122 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
